b_date": "2025-01-03 14:28:45", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747448", "title": "Petrobras: Expanding Production At Attractive Breakeven Economics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lula Attends Launch of Petrobras Cultural Selection 2024\" data-id=\"2026351694\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Wagner Meier/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Performance Assessment</h2> <p>The Brazilian oil company Petrobras (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PBR\" title=\"Petr\u00f3leo Brasileiro S.A. - Petrobras\">PBR</a></span>) has been a bit of a miss for me since my last update 1.75 years ago as it has handily outperformed the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2026351694/image_2026351694.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747448-petrobras-stock-expanding-production-at-attractive-breakeven-economics", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 14:23:48", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747444", "title": "Pfizer: A Step-By-Step Strategy Before Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture class=\"highlighted_text\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pfizer HQ in New York City\" data-id=\"1491484031\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1101px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1491484031/image_1491484031.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 1